From 510b97ce6af3f5c1be6c53668b1be0d0ffcfea9e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Slick <slick@slicksync.local>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 07:32:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: lighter Nuvio badge, Nebula theme (replaces Lagoon),
 better Stremio check diagnostics

- Nuvio badge orange half opacity 0.22 -> 0.10, less heavy
- Lagoon theme replaced with Nebula: Midnight's dark blue-black
  structure, Slick's violet-to-cyan accent gradient instead of amber
- checkStremioAuth now surfaces Stremio's actual response detail on
  failure instead of a generic 'rejected' message, and specifically
  flags rate-limit responses separately from real credential
  failures - the generic message made it impossible to tell a
  genuinely wrong password apart from a transient API issue

Bump to 1.9.21, changelog entry added.
